  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK487">
<l>poḷḷeṉa vāṅkē puṟamvērār kālampārt</l>
<l>tuḷvērppa roḷḷi yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wise will not immediately and hastily shew out their anger; they will watch their time, and restrain it within.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
